name: Corneo's Aerith (FF7) Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Aerith Gainsborough from Final Fantasy VII (essentially both original and remake together).

As many of her appearances show the pink dress in a very light color, it's best to prompt this with green eyes, pink dress, corneo_aerith as it sometimes (though rare) doesn't get the dress or eye color right by itself.

v2 example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!

I now have a running poll for the next character embed to work on at https://strawpoll.com/master-corneo
You can comment with any requests to add but it needs to be someone with enough fan art available to train on, and also a character I'd want to do!

modelVersions.description: Update along with my other updated embeddings, fixes some problems in training data, making the result more accurate to the character
